Eva Zou MSc
Operations Manager of True Partner Capital Advisor, holds a MSc in Finance from the Chinese University of Hong Kong, as well as a MPhil in Electronics and Computer Engineering from the Hong Kong University of Science and Technology. She joined True Partner Capital Advisor in 2014. Eva is currently responsible for the mid-office and operations of the Funds of True Partner Capital Advisor. Furthermore, Eva serves as the liaison with the Prime Brokers and service providers.
Eva Zou on LinkedIn
