Adam Biro MSc
Senior Web Developer of True Partner Capital Advisor, has been writing software for 15 years in various programming languages and technologies, working for multinational companies like Citibank, TATA Consultancy Services, Saen Options and Payvision. As a student his first software won first prize of the Hungarian National Scientific and Innovation Competition for Youth in 1997. As a professional Adam has built up a solid and all-round IT knowledge, working in different roles as: database developer, web developer, backend developer, android mobile developer, as well as technical lead and system integrator. He holds a MSc in Economics, a BSc in Foreign Economics, an Associate Degree in Software Design and Development and is a Microsoft Certified Professional Developer (MCPD) in web technologies.
