Ed Donnellan
Chief Compliance Officer at True Partner Capital Advisor, has over 35 years’ experience in the financial services industry, with broad-based experience in legal, compliance and management roles. His career began in market regulation at the CBOE, MSE (now CHX) and CME. He was president of a global futures clearing broker and SEVP of a primary dealer. Ed has also served in senior management positions as well as on the boards of several hedge fund managers and proprietary trading firms. He is a member of the Illinois Bar.
