Doris Wong BSc
CFO of True Partner Capital Advisor, has worked as an accountant since 2004. She started at International Credit Management Consultancy Limited as an accounts clerk, then moved to Primasia Corporate Services Limited as assistant accountant and promoted to be accountant and leader of a team responsible for all accounting, preparation of monthly reports for management for in-house companies and clients companies, monitoring company cash flow, liaise with external auditors and company secretary. Doris joined True Partner in 2011. Doris holds a Bachelor of Commerce (Accounting) degree from the University of Technology, Sydney. Doris is member of the Association of Chartered Certified Accountants. Doris is part of the management team of True Partner Capital Advisor.
